{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775880665532,"sessionID":"ses_285499d3bffeOS6QnxS0CK1eWh","part":{"id":"prt_d7ab7b0ec001m6qde7y4La76mV","messageID":"msg_d7ab72d53001zn7Im3pCu2FnV9","sessionID":"ses_285499d3bffeOS6QnxS0CK1eWh","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:14","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-018/tasks.md","content":"# AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 (Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller)\n\n> **Module:** `pkg/agentd`  \n> **Language:** Go  \n> **Size:** S  \n> **Stage:** ST-3 (Design) Completed → ST-4 (Implementation)  \n> **Base Spec:** client-go library (deployment/client-go.md), idle-cleanup/design.md\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\nAR-018 implements the Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller that watches `Sandbox` custom resources and deletes them when they have been inactive beyond a configured grace period (15 minutes). The controller uses controller-runtime for reconciliation and reads the `last-activity-time` annotation to determine idle status.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.1 — Package Structure and Constants\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.1.1 | Create `pkg/agentd/` directory structure | Directory exists | 0.25h |\n| 4.1.2 | Create `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go` | File compiles | 0.5h |\n| 4.1.3 | Define `SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute` constant | Constant defined and exported | 0.25h |\n| 4.1.4 | Define `RequeueAfterParseError = 30 * time.Second` constant | Constant defined and exported | 0.25h |\n| 4.1.5 | Add package-level doc comment | `go doc ./pkg/agentd` shows overview | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Package structure compiles with constants defined.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.2 — Reconciler Struct and Interface\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.2.1 | Define `Reconciler` struct with `client.Client` and `Scheme *runtime.Scheme` fields | Struct matches delta-spec | 0.5h |\n| 4.2.2 | Import required packages (`sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client`, `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime`) | All imports resolve | 0.25h |\n| 4.2.3 | Import `workloadmanager` package for annotation key constant | Import path correct | 0.25h |\n| 4.2.4 | Import Sandbox types from `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1` | Type references compile | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Reconciler struct defined with correct fields and imports.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.3 — Reconcile Method Implementation\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.3.1 | Implement `Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request) (ctrl.Result, error)` signature | Method signature matches spec | 0.25h |\n| 4.3.2 | Fetch Sandbox: `sandbox := &sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}`; `r.Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, sandbox)` | Get call compiles | 0.5h |\n| 4.3.3 | Handle `IsNotFound` error from Get: return `ctrl.Result{}, nil` | NotFound returns empty result | 0.5h |\n| 4.3.4 | Handle other Get errors: return `ctrl.Result{}, err` | Other errors returned | 0.25h |\n| 4.3.5 | Read annotation: `sandbox.Annotations[workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey]` | Annotation key constant used | 0.25h |\n| 4.3.6 | Handle missing/empty annotation: return `ctrl.Result{}, nil` | No requeue for missing annotation | 0.25h |\n| 4.3.7 | Parse RFC3339 timestamp with `time.Parse(time.RFC3339, lastActivityStr)` | Parsing logic implemented | 0.5h |\n| 4.3.8 | Handle parse error: return `ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}, err` | Parse error requeues with 30s | 0.5h |\n| 4.3.9 | Compute `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)` | Expiration calculation correct | 0.25h |\n| 4.3.10 | Check expiration: `if time.Now().After(expirationTime)` | Time comparison correct | 0.25h |\n| 4.3.11 | Delete expired sandbox: `r.Delete(ctx, sandbox)` | Delete call implemented | 0.5h |\n| 4.3.12 | Handle delete `IsNotFound`: return `ctrl.Result{}, nil` | Idempotent delete handling | 0.25h |\n| 4.3.13 | Handle other delete errors: return `ctrl.Result{}, err` | Other delete errors returned | 0.25h |\n| 4.3.14 | Requeue for future expiration: `ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}` | Future requeue logic correct | 0.5h |\n| 4.3.15 | Return empty result when delete succeeds | `return ctrl.Result{}, nil` | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Reconcile method fully implements idle cleanup algorithm per delta-spec.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.4 — SetupWithManager Implementation\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.4.1 | Implement `SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error` method | Method signature correct | 0.25h |\n| 4.4.2 | Create controller: `ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{})` | Builder pattern correct | 0.5h |\n| 4.4.3 | Complete controller: `.Complete(r)` | Controller completes with reconciler | 0.25h |\n| 4.4.4 | Return error from SetupWithManager | Error propagated correctly | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Controller registration with manager works correctly.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.5 — Unit Tests — Reconcile Scenarios\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.5.1 | Create `pkg/agentd/reconciler_test.go` with build tag | File compiles with `go test` | 0.5h |\n| 4.5.2 | Write `TestReconcile_SandboxNotFound` — Get returns NotFound | Returns empty result, no error | 0.5h |\n| 4.5.3 | Write `TestReconcile_GetError` — Get returns other error | Returns error, no requeue | 0.5h |\n| 4.5.4 | Write `TestReconcile_NoAnnotation` — Sandbox without last-activity-time | Returns empty result, no delete | 0.5h |\n| 4.5.5 | Write `TestReconcile_EmptyAnnotation` — Empty annotation value | Returns empty result, no delete | 0.5h |\n| 4.5.6 | Write `TestReconcile_InvalidTimestamp` — Malformed RFC3339 | Returns RequeueAfter: 30s, with error | 0.5h |\n| 4.5.7 | Write `TestReconcile_NotExpired` — Last activity 5 minutes ago | Returns RequeueAfter: ~10m, no delete | 0.5h |\n| 4.5.8 | Write `TestReconcile_JustExpired` — Last activity exactly 15 minutes ago | Delete called, returns empty result | 0.5h |\n| 4.5.9 | Write `TestReconcile_Expired` — Last activity 20 minutes ago | Delete called, returns empty result | 0.5h |\n| 4.5.10 | Write `TestReconcile_DeleteNotFound` — Delete returns NotFound | Returns empty result, no error | 0.5h |\n| 4.5.11 | Write `TestReconcile_DeleteError` — Delete returns other error | Returns error for retry | 0.5h |\n| 4.5.12 | Write `TestReconcile_FutureExpirationRequeue` — Verify RequeueAfter calculation | RequeueAfter matches time.Until | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** All reconcile scenario tests pass with >85% coverage.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.6 — Unit Tests — Mock Client Setup\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.6.1 | Create mock client implementing `client.Client` interface | Mock compiles | 0.5h |\n| 4.6.2 | Implement mock `Get` method with configurable return values | Returns configured Sandbox/error | 0.5h |\n| 4.6.3 | Implement mock `Delete` method with configurable return values | Returns configured error | 0.5h |\n| 4.6.4 | Create test helpers for building Sandbox objects with annotations | Helper functions work | 0.5h |\n| 4.6.5 | Create test helpers for timestamp generation (past, future, RFC3339) | Time helpers accurate | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Mock infrastructure supports all reconciler tests.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.7 — Binary Entry Point (cmd/agentd)\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.7.1 | Create `cmd/agentd/` directory structure | Directory exists | 0.25h |\n| 4.7.2 | Create `cmd/agentd/main.go` | File compiles | 0.5h |\n| 4.7.3 | Import required packages (controller-runtime, sandbox types, core k8s) | All imports resolve | 0.5h |\n| 4.7.4 | Initialize scheme builder: `schemeBuilder := runtime.NewSchemeBuilder()` | Scheme builder created | 0.25h |\n| 4.7.5 | Register core Kubernetes scheme: `utilruntime.Must(scheme.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))` | Core types registered | 0.5h |\n| 4.7.6 | Register Sandbox scheme: `utilruntime.Must(sandboxv1alpha1.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))` | Sandbox types registered | 0.5h |\n| 4.7.7 | Create manager: `ctrl.NewManager(ctrl.GetConfigOrDie(), ctrl.Options{...})` | Manager created with options | 0.5h |\n| 4.7.8 | Configure manager scheme: `Scheme: schemeBuilder` | Scheme passed to manager | 0.25h |\n| 4.7.9 | Disable metrics: `Metrics: metricsserver.Options{BindAddress: \"0\"}` | Metrics disabled | 0.25h |\n| 4.7.10 | Disable health probes: `HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\"` | Health probes disabled | 0.25h |\n| 4.7.11 | Create reconciler: `&agentd.Reconciler{Client: mgr.GetClient(), Scheme: mgr.GetScheme()}` | Reconciler initialized | 0.5h |\n| 4.7.12 | Setup controller: `reconciler.SetupWithManager(mgr)` | Controller registered | 0.5h |\n| 4.7.13 | Start manager: `mgr.Start(ctrl.SetupSignalHandler())` | Manager starts with signal handler | 0.5h |\n| 4.7.14 | Handle manager start errors | Errors logged and process exits | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Binary compiles and can be started (integration tests verify full functionality).\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.8 — Documentation\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.8.1 | Add package-level GoDoc for `pkg/agentd` | Overview documentation complete | 0.5h |\n| 4.8.2 | Document `Reconciler` struct with inline comments | Purpose and fields documented | 0.25h |\n| 4.8.3 | Document `Reconcile` method with algorithm description | Algorithm steps documented | 0.5h |\n| 4.8.4 | Document `SetupWithManager` method | Purpose and usage documented | 0.25h |\n| 4.8.5 | Add code comments for non-trivial logic in Reconcile | Inline comments explain decisions | 0.5h |\n| 4.8.6 | Document constants (`SessionExpirationTimeout`, `RequeueAfterParseError`) | Constants explained | 0.25h |\n| 4.8.7 | Add README or doc.go explaining how to run agentd | Usage documentation | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Code is well-documented with GoDoc.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.9 — Build and Integration Verification\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.9.1 | Verify `go build ./pkg/agentd/...` succeeds | Package builds without errors | 0.25h |\n| 4.9.2 | Verify `go build ./cmd/agentd/...` succeeds | Binary builds without errors | 0.25h |\n| 4.9.3 | Run unit tests: `go test ./pkg/agentd/... -v` | All tests pass | 0.5h |\n| 4.9.4 | Run tests with coverage: `go test ./pkg/agentd/... -cover` | Coverage >85% | 0.25h |\n| 4.9.5 | Run race detector: `go test ./pkg/agentd/... -race` | No race conditions detected | 0.5h |\n| 4.9.6 | Run go vet: `go vet ./pkg/agentd/...` | No issues reported | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** All build and quality checks pass.\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| Phase | Tasks | Est. Hours |\n|-------|-------|------------|\n| ST-4.1: Package Structure | 5 | 1.75h |\n| ST-4.2: Reconciler Struct | 4 | 1.25h |\n| ST-4.3: Reconcile Method | 15 | 5.5h |\n| ST-4.4: SetupWithManager | 4 | 1.25h |\n| ST-4.5: Unit Tests (Scenarios) | 12 | 6h |\n| ST-4.6: Unit Tests (Mock Setup) | 5 | 2.5h |\n| ST-4.7: Binary Entry Point | 14 | 6h |\n| ST-4.8: Documentation | 7 | 3h |\n| ST-4.9: Build Verification | 6 | 2.5h |\n| **Total** | **72** | **30.75h** |\n\n---\n\n## File Deliverables Checklist\n\n- [ ] `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go` — Reconciler implementation\n- [ ] `pkg/agentd/reconciler_test.go` — Unit tests for reconciler\n- [ ] `cmd/agentd/main.go` — Binary entry point\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n```bash\n# Build verification\nmake build\n# OR:\ngo build ./pkg/agentd/...\ngo build ./cmd/agentd/...\n\n# Unit tests\ngo test ./pkg/agentd/... -v\n\n# With coverage\ngo test ./pkg/agentd/... -cover\n\n# Race detection\ngo test ./pkg/agentd/... -race\n\n# Static analysis\ngo vet ./pkg/agentd/...\n\n# Binary build\ngo build -o bin/agentd ./cmd/agentd\n\n# Run binary (requires k8s config)\n./bin/agentd\n```\n\n---\n\n## Definition of Done\n\n- [ ] All 72 tasks complete\n- [ ] Reconciler implements full idle cleanup algorithm per delta-spec\n- [ ] SetupWithManager registers controller correctly\n- [ ] Unit tests pass (>85% coverage)\n- [ ] All scenario tests from delta-spec pass\n- [ ] Race detector clean\n- [ ] `go build ./pkg/agentd/...` succeeds\n- [ ] `go build ./cmd/agentd/...` succeeds\n- [ ] Documentation complete with GoDoc\n- [ ] Binary starts successfully (integration test)\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Purpose |\n|------------|---------|\n| `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` | Controller-runtime framework |\n| `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1` | Sandbox CRD types |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors` | Kubernetes API errors |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime` | Kubernetes runtime types |\n| `k8s.io/client-go/kubernetes/scheme` | Core Kubernetes scheme |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager` | Annotation key constants |\n\n---\n\n## Design Notes\n\n- **Timeout:** 15 minutes hardcoded (`SessionExpirationTimeout`)\n- **Parse error retry:** 30 seconds (`RequeueAfterParseError`)\n- **Annotation key:** Uses `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey` constant\n- **Timestamp format:** RFC3339 (e.g., \"2024-01-15T10:30:00Z\")\n- **Idempotency:** NotFound errors on Get/Delete treated as success\n- **Future requeue:** Uses `time.Until(expirationTime)` for precise scheduling\n- **Metrics:** Disabled (BindAddress: \"0\")\n- **Health probes:** Disabled (HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\")\n- **Signal handling:** Uses `ctrl.SetupSignalHandler()` for graceful shutdown\n\n---\n\n## Algorithm Reference (from delta-spec)\n\n```\n1. Get Sandbox by NamespacedName\n2. If IsNotFound(err) → return (Result{}, nil)\n3. If other get error → return (Result{}, err)\n4. Read last-activity-time annotation\n5. If missing/empty → return (Result{}, nil)\n6. Parse RFC3339 timestamp\n7. If parse error → return (Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}, err)\n8. Compute expirationTime = lastActivity + 15 minutes\n9. If time.Now().After(expirationTime):\n   - Delete Sandbox\n   - If delete NotFound → return (Result{}, nil)\n   - If delete error → return (Result{}, err)\n   - Else → return (Result{}, nil)\n10. Else → return (Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil)\n```\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/pkg/workloadmanager/controller/reconciler.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/go.mod":[{"range":{"start":{"line":18,"character":42},"end":{"line":18,"character":53}},"severity":2,"source":"go mod tidy","message":"github.com/alicebob/miniredis/v2 should be direct"},{"range":{"start":{"line":35,"character":31},"end":{"line":35,"character":42}},"severity":2,"source":"go mod tidy","message":"github.com/google/uuid should be direct"}]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-018/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-018/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775880665520,"end":1775880665529}}}}
